name: Gothic Fest VI

image.alt: Gothic Fest VI festival poster for the event on September 2, 2017, featuring international gothic rock bands.

body: On Saturday 2.9.2017 at Burg Sternberg will take place “This is Gothic Festival VI”, an international festival with bands from the Gothic Rock , Post-Punk , New Wave scene.
artists: Salvation AMP, Kadeadkas, Dark Sun Bright, Come With Reverse
